data.description: This Beautiful home on 2.13 wooded acres is set back from the road to enjoy your privacy. Well maintained yard with above ground pool with fenced area to allow pets to enjoy the outdoors.  The two car garage has ample space for parking as well as work benches and storage with partially finished room above. There is a family room when enter the home from the garage with sliding door to you large deck looking over the beautiful back yard with electric retractable awning as well as a front entry door. The dining room and living room feature an open floor plan with cathedral ceilings with solid wood beams a large picture window looks out over your front yard. The kitchen is open to the dining room. The first has a full bath as well as two bedrooms and the laundry closet with washer and dryer. Head up the stair to the landing over looking the lining and dining rooms before entering the 3rd bedroom featuring sky lights, closets and a half bathroom.
